'Oh'

730
00:44:19,156 --> 00:44:20,616
(Kim Shin)
Since I was six years old, all along

731
00:44:21,325 --> 00:44:22,201
(Deokhwa)
Oh

732
00:44:24,286 --> 00:44:25,204
No

