00:45:29,476 --> 00:45:30,894
I got an umbrella.

757
00:45:31,520 --> 00:45:32,855
Is this your first time
seeing an umbrella?

758
00:45:33,647 --> 00:45:34,731
Thank you. Oh my, in my life I

