should have an umbrella too, tsk.

760
00:45:39,069 --> 00:45:41,947
[Chewing on
snacks] Ah, it's soggy.

761
00:45:42,614 --> 00:45:43,866
(Euntak) Should I
give you a new one?

762
00:45:43,991 --> 00:45:46,952
(Sunny) No thanks,
I know this flavor.

763
00:45:47,035 --> 00:45:48,120
It's a hassle to chew on a
new one. Where are you going?

764
00:45:48,203 --> 00:45:50,622
That kind of line
is for the boss only.

765
00:45:51,081 --> 00:45:54,126
You, the part-timer, can slack off
and have fun when I'm not around.

766
00:45:54,209 --> 00:45:57,963
