767
00:45:58,046 --> 00:45:59,715
You should work harder when they're not around

768
00:45:59,798 --> 00:46:02,384
(Sunny)
If you work harder when they're not around

769
00:46:02,551 --> 00:46:04,428
the boss won't know, part-timer

