00:46:06,889 --> 00:46:08,849
Oh man, that's cool

772
00:46:09,308 --> 00:46:11,560
[The door opens and closes with a click]
Take care

773
00:46:12,478 --> 00:46:13,437
(Sunny)
Huh?

774
00:46:14,354 --> 00:46:15,731
(Fortune-teller)
Ah, triplets

775
00:46:16,315 --> 00:46:17,691
I'm the youngest

776
00:46:17,774 --> 00:46:18,650
[THE FORTUNE-TELLER SMILES SLIGHTLY]

777
00:46:18,734 --> 00:46:20,319
Let's see, let's see

778
00:46:20,402 --> 00:46:22,154
What brought you here?

779
00:46:22,237 --> 00:46:24,448
Isn't that something you need to guess?

780
00:46:25,574 --> 00:46:27,242
What isn't going well?

781
00:46:27,326 --> 00:46:30,329
(Sunny)
If things were going well, I wouldn't be here
I’d be sitting in the store counting money

782
00:46:30,579 --> 00:46:32,539
[EXCITING MUSIC]

783
00:46:34,082 --> 00:46:37,377
(Fortune-teller)
Oh dear, for your fortune
you have no luck with kids at all

784
00:46:37,461 --> 00:46:39,046
